<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 12:28:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>伦敦证券交易所数据显示，本月外国资金正在撤离中国以外的亚洲股市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/foreign-money-is-leaving-asian-equities-ex-china-this-month-lseg-data-shows-2024-10-09/</link><description>由于对股票估值过高和中东冲突的担忧促使投资者获利了结，外国资金本月正在离开亚洲股市（不包括中国）。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 12:24:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/foreign-money-is-leaving-asian-equities-ex-china-this-month-lseg-data-shows-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体报道，欧盟对中国电动汽车做出裁决后，中欧团队将继续进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-eu-team-continue-talks-after-blocs-ruling-chinese-evs-state-media-reports-2024-10-09/</link><description>官方通讯社新华社周三援引知情人士的话报道称，中国最近与美国和欧盟就电动汽车贸易问题进行了“密集沟通”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 12:07:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-eu-team-continue-talks-after-blocs-ruling-chinese-evs-state-media-reports-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>部长表示，中国期待日本新内阁的“新氛围”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-looks-forward-new-atmosphere-with-new-japan-cabinet-minister-says-2024-10-09/</link><description>据中国中央电视台报道，中国外交部长王毅周三对日本新任外长岩屋武表示，北京期待日本新内阁营造“新氛围”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 12:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-looks-forward-new-atmosphere-with-new-japan-cabinet-minister-says-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉9月中国产电动汽车销量同比增长19.2%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-made-ev-sales-grow-192-yy-sept-2024-10-09/</link><description>中国乘用车协会(CPCA)周三的数据显示，美国汽车制造商特斯拉9月份中国制造的电动汽车销量同比增长19.2%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 11:15:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-made-ev-sales-grow-192-yy-sept-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰驻土耳其特使表示，乌克兰希望在年底前举行包括俄罗斯在内的和平峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-eyes-peace-summit-by-year-end-that-includes-russia-envoy-turkey-says-2024-10-09/</link><description>乌克兰驻土耳其大使周三表示，乌克兰计划在今年年底前组织一次新的和平峰会，并希望俄罗斯参加这次会议，但排除了在会议上与莫斯科进行任何直接双边会谈的可能性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 11:08:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-eyes-peace-summit-by-year-end-that-includes-russia-envoy-turkey-says-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：随着石油回落、中国撤退，米尔顿做好准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-09/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 10:16:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟委员会主席：匈牙利对俄对华政策构成安全风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-commission-chief-hungarys-russia-china-policies-pose-security-risk-2024-10-09/</link><description>欧盟委员会主席乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩周三在一次异常直率的演讲中批评布达佩斯与俄罗斯和中国的关系，称匈牙利正在将欧洲安全置于危险之中。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 10:07:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-commission-chief-hungarys-russia-china-policies-pose-security-risk-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>除了政治之外，中国的导弹试验反映了军事需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/beyond-politics-chinas-missile-test-reflects-military-need-2024-10-09/</link><description>从一枚导弹谨慎地运送超过 1,000 公里（620 英里）到发射场，到使用远程基地和卫星跟踪它从海南岛到南太平洋，中国 9 月的洲际弹道导弹飞行标志着对作战必要性的一次考验。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 10:04:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/beyond-politics-chinas-missile-test-reflects-military-need-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>分析师称奢侈品不太可能成为中国欧盟贸易报复的下一个目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/luxury-goods-unlikely-be-next-target-chinas-eu-trade-retaliation-analysts-say-2024-10-09/</link><description>在欧盟决定对中国电动汽车征收关税后，投资者担心爱马仕手袋和迪奥露跟鞋可能成为北京的下一个报复目标，欧洲奢侈品牌股价下跌，但分析师表示，此举不太可能。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 09:57:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/luxury-goods-unlikely-be-next-target-chinas-eu-trade-retaliation-analysts-say-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>芬兰总统将在对中国进行国事访问时会见习近平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/finlands-president-meet-xi-state-visit-china-2024-10-09/</link><description>芬兰政府周三表示，芬兰总统亚历山大·斯塔布将于10月28日至31日对中国进行国事访问，并会见中国国家主席习近平和其他政府高级官员。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 09:07:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/finlands-president-meet-xi-state-visit-china-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国称对欧盟白兰地反倾销是合法贸易措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-says-anti-dumping-move-eu-brandy-is-legitimate-trade-measure-2024-10-09/</link><description>在实施临时限制措施的第二天，商务部周三表示，中国对欧盟进口白兰地的反倾销措施是“合法的贸易救济措施”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 09:06:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-says-anti-dumping-move-eu-brandy-is-legitimate-trade-measure-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国9月银行贷款将因政策支持而增加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-september-bank-lending-set-rise-policy-support-2024-10-09/</link><description>路透周三的一项民意调查显示，随着央行加大刺激力度，推动陷入困境的经济实现今年的增长目标，中国 9 月份新增人民币贷款可能较 8 月份大幅增加。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 08:51:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-september-bank-lending-set-rise-policy-support-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国称针对欧盟白兰地反倾销措施合法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-says-anti-dumping-move-against-eu-brandy-legit-trade-measures-2024-10-09/</link><description>中国商务部周三表示，中国对欧盟进口白兰地采取的反倾销措施是“合法的贸易救济措施”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 06:44:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-says-anti-dumping-move-against-eu-brandy-legit-trade-measures-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，英国外交大臣拉米将访华以重启两国关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/british-foreign-secretary-lammy-visit-china-bid-reset-ties-sources-say-2024-10-09/</link><description>据知情人士透露，英国外交大臣戴维·拉米将于下周访问中国，新工党政府寻求减少与世界第二大经济体的对抗性关系，并恢复贸易和投资谈判。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 06:29:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/british-foreign-secretary-lammy-visit-china-bid-reset-ties-sources-say-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>沃尔沃汽车副首席执行官将因管理层改组而辞职</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-deputy-ceo-step-down-management-reshuffle-2024-10-09/</link><description>沃尔沃汽车周三表示，其副首席执行官比约恩·安沃尔(Bjorn Annwall)将离开该集团，作为重组的一部分，该重组旨在提高组织的简单性、速度和协作性，并降低组织的复杂性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 06:13:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-deputy-ceo-step-down-management-reshuffle-2024-10-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>